H0.text: Nerve fibers are what else, along with blood vessels, are contained in Haversian canals.

H1.text: Muscle fibers are what else, besides blood vessels, that Haversian canals contain.

H2.text: Synovial fluid is contained in Haversian canals along with blood vessels.

H3.text: Collagen fibers are found in Haversian canals along with blood vessels.

A4.text: Each Haversian canal generally contains one or two capillaries and many nerve fibres.
